  {
    "index": 3,
    "hash": "LWY8xMpTV3Hgh0s3Y20chHO6QBc=",
    "timestampUtcMs": "2026-05-13T13:00:28.000Z",
    "action": {
      "type": "SET_CONTENT",
      "input": {
        "content": "## What shipped\n\nChat file sharing is feature-complete for the current scope:\n\n- **Raw file uploads** via `swarm-file.ts` with cached ACT grantees - images, PDF, audio, video, text.\n- **Inline previews** in `message-bubble.tsx` and `files-tab.tsx` - image / GIF / PDF iframe / audio / video / text.\n- **Drag-and-drop** via `ThreadDropZone` in `chat-panel.tsx`.\n- **Lightbox + universal preview modal** in the Files tab, portaled with `data-chat-overlay` so the chat panel stays open underneath.\n- **External Swarm-link previews** for `bzz://<hash>` and `https://.../bzz/<hash>` - detected in `MessageBody`, probed via `ChatManager.probeSwarmReference`.\n- **200 MB upload cap** - `MAX_FILE_SIZE` enforced in adapter and client.\n- **Video codec pre-flight** with `canPlayType` and an `onError` download fallback on `<video>`.\n- **Broad mime-guess** - MKV, FLV, 3GP, TS/MTS, WMV, VOB, etc. in `mime-guess.ts`.\n- **Unread badge** on sidebar chat icon via `useUnreadCount` + custom-event dispatch.\n\n## Implication\n\nThe media-sharing surface is done; remaining gap is Swarm-link detection inside the Files tab list.",
        "updatedAt": "2026-05-13T13:00:28.000Z"
      },
      "timestampUtcMs": "2026-05-13T13:00:28.000Z"
    }
  },
